  David,
   
  Try to make sure your files are in mp3 format (smaller file sizes than wav) and keep posts under 500kb total thats usually about what the limit is here on the yahoo group for individual files/uploads.
   
  If you are doing all of that and still seeing script errors when you upload then most likely its a browser conflict, you could try using a different browser or updating it might help. Good luck!
   
  Misty
